{"tid":1370356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727 元朗教會休息站","createTime":"2019-07-27T03:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T03:41:01.000Z","uid":288254,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1750d5507dc2f79fb16999dcfd3cc0c376a157f","tid":1370356,"uid":288254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:24:39.000Z","msg":"行完街倦就去休息一下<br />\n<br />\n【元朗 屯門 天水圍 聖堂 2019.7.27週六開放情況】<br />\n（公教報訊）元朗，屯門和天水圍區聖堂七月廿七日（週六）除原有的提前主日彌撒外，其開放情況如下，附堂區連結：<br />\n<br />\n＝＝聖伯多祿聖保祿堂（元朗）<br />\n27/7&mdash;&mdash;祈禱和反思日<br />\n上午8時：明供朝拜聖體（小聖堂）<br />\n下午3時： 慈悲時刻（大聖堂）<br />\n下午5時：彌撒（大聖堂 &ndash; 英語）<br />\n晚上6時30 分：彌撒（大聖堂 &ndash; 粵語）<br />\n由晚上8 時開始：祈禱和反思時間（大聖堂）<br />\n歡迎大家隨時來臨一起參與祈禱。<br />\n地址：新界元朗青山公路201號屏山段<br />\n電話：24760887<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SSPETERANDPAUL.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSSPETERANDPAUL.HK&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd3No2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=dae9ace8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SSPETERANDPAUL.HK</a><br />\n<br />\n＝＝屯門贖世主堂<br />\n27/7下午3時起明供聖體，為香港社會祈禱。<br />\n同時，亦會開放地方給有需要人士作休息之用。<br />\n地址：屯門鄉事會路二號<br />\n電話：2459 6510<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/holyredeemerchurchhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fholyredeemerchurchhk&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd3No2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=2e1c2da5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/holyredeemerchurchhk</a><br />\n<br />\n＝＝天水圍聖葉理諾堂<br />\n27/7通宵開放至翌日<br />\n作祈禱/輔導/護理/休息之用<br />\n地址：天水圍天美街6號<br />\n電話：2448 8332<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stjeromeschurch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstjeromeschurch&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd3No2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=1072c185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stjeromeschurch</a>"},{"pid":"c53d7d5c5830e3a4bed554b0822066b30a94ec65","tid":1370356,"uid":248000,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl